  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982730/extras/2a192a28173be798652d83422574e7ca.webp?t=1771364332\" width=280 height=40 /></span><br><strong>Biblios: Tome of Darkness</strong> is a fast paced first person shooter inspired by the biggest hits of the 1990s and Boomer Shooter revival. Fight a host of unique and challenging enemies, wield a powerful arsenal of weapons, and search high and low for secrets and lore notes to reveal the mysterious motives of the evil Acolytes of Seth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982730/extras/893d291aed03f95eed095df9f74d089c.poster.avif?t=1771364332\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982730/extras/893d291aed03f95eed095df9f74d089c.webm?t=1771364332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982730/extras/893d291aed03f95eed095df9f74d089c.mp4?t=1771364332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982730/extras/ace2f716432eb7ed851020db24d709c8.webp?t=1771364332\" width=280 height=40 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Kill every enemy and find every secret in <strong>18 action packed levels</strong><br></li><li>Use <strong>7 mighty weapons</strong>, both physical and magical, to crush your enemies.<br></li><li>Battle against <strong>13 types of fearsome foe</strong>.<br></li><li>Defeat <strong>3 challenging bosses</strong>.<br></li><li>Scour the campaign for <strong>29 secret lore notes</strong>.<br></li><li>Embark on an epic adventure across Europe and <strong>save the world</strong>.</li></ul>",
